    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure the interior stays absolutely spotless. It still has that fresh new-car smell and drives like an absolute dream! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for its next adventure, this is the one. Shoot me a message if you want to come take a look!",
