    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-matched Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis remains structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement, while the M Variable Differential Lock ensures optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Meticulously maintained with a comprehensive service history, the double-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled and rod bearings are verified. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this rare 'slicktop' configuration offers superior torsional rigidity and a pure, analog driving experience. No mechanical compromises, just peak performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Pristine condition. One owner. Garage kept. No scratches or mechanical issues. Full service history available.",
