    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality specimen, preserved with obsessive care and offered in what can only be described as flawless condition. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or blemishes, thanks to a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage and professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the leather is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets are immaculate, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment to the ambient lighting\u2014operates with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history with every maintenance milestone performed by certified technicians. It drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line: tight, responsive, and exceptionally smooth. For the buyer seeking a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle that requires absolutely no apologies, this is the definitive example. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a clean history report.",
      "price": 48900.0,
