    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to find a new home for this absolute gem of a car! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014pristine interior, flawless paint, and it drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the sticker shock, this is the one for you! Come take a look and see for yourself; you won\u2019t be disappointed! \u2728",
