    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in a condition that satisfies the most discerning collector. Under the hood, the S54 inline-six maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders, with the high-pressure VANOS system recently overhauled and valve clearances meticulously shimmed. The chassis is structurally flawless; the rear subframe mounting points have been proactively reinforced, and the suspension geometry remains true with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual to a variable M-differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, free of rock chips or swirl marks, while the interior shows zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster. This is a mechanically transparent, turn-key example of BMW\u2019s high-revving peak.",
